  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Roll the Dice\"</strong> is a tabletop dice game that combines strategy and luck, taking you into a world full of changes, challenges, and surprises. On an 8x6 grid, players roll dice, activate cells, and trigger item combinations to accumulate points and aim to surpass their previous achievements in each level. Each turn, based on the dice rolls and positions, players use carefully designed items and set effects to strategize and win.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose the props or arrows you think are appropriate and adjust their positions in the construction table so that they can play the greatest role</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/e2ce78dc6473043ac26ed5e866de4c47.poster.avif?t=1741104445\" width=800 height=602 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/e2ce78dc6473043ac26ed5e866de4c47.webm?t=1741104445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/e2ce78dc6473043ac26ed5e866de4c47.mp4?t=1741104445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect and activate the suit to provide you with powerful gains</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/812c594f53ed08d7528a60cd2a7e44d3.poster.avif?t=1741104445\" width=320 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/812c594f53ed08d7528a60cd2a7e44d3.webm?t=1741104445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Various dice escort your way forward</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/248bc773d240e985b2289e78f745e636.apng?t=1741104445\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/248bc773d240e985b2289e78f745e636.poster.avif?t=1741104445\" class=\"bb_img\" width=470 height=140 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The level difficulty is randomly generated in each round, making the journey full of thrills</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/1ae82afdbe0256aebd9e6370f122bceb.poster.avif?t=1741104445\" width=590 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/1ae82afdbe0256aebd9e6370f122bceb.webm?t=1741104445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229240/extras/1ae82afdbe0256aebd9e6370f122bceb.mp4?t=1741104445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Here you can experience</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >75 props with different effects, strategic choices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24 arrows with different effects, auxiliary gains</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30 dice with different effects, increase the upper limit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random level difficulty in each round, thrilling challenge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good luck!!!</p></li></ul>",
